http://www.atr.org:80/lead-inst/bridge.html 204.71.237.87 19970209220213 text/html 6046
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 22:02:57 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 07-Aug-96 17:06:52 GMT
