<p>
<a name="sleazy">
<center><h2>Sleazy Talk = Truth</h2></center>

<dd><big>"</big>We are not responsible for drug abuse.  We don't cause teen pregnancy.  These government officials are more responsible for creating what they see on TV than we are.  We just tell the truth.<big>"</big>

<p>
Talk show host Charles Perez (November 11 TV Guide)
<p>
<font size=-1>-- An excerpt from the Media Research Center's Entertainment Division</font>
<p>
