<a name="energizer">
<center><h2>MRC's Energizer Book</h2>
<h3>And That's the Way It Isn't keeps going strong</h3></center>
<dd><big>E</big>dited by Brent Bozell  and Brent Baker, <i><b>And That's the Way It Isn't: A Reference Guide to Media Bias</b></i> demonstrates conclusively that America's most influential media outlets report the news through a liberal prism. 
<dd>With reprints, excerpts, and summaries of more than 40 studies conducted over a number of years, this book provides the most thorough analysis ever compiled proving the liberal political slant in the national press.
<dd>This reference has been so popular and successful that it has been reprinted seven times. The National Review magazine and the Leadership Institute have both helped distribute thousands of copies through their organizations since the first printing in 1990. 
<dd>To date we have distributed almost <b>45,000 books</b> nationally! We are offering this reference guide to our members at a special <b>Members Only</b> discounted price.
