<font size=+1><b>Brent Bozell's column is nationally syndicated by Creators Syndicate. If your local paper doesn't carry Brent's column call or write to its editor and ask for it. Or you can contact us here and we'll give you more information on getting the column in your local paper.</b></font>
</blockquote>
</body>
