http://www.atr.org:80/townhall/FRC/perspective/pv96b3dr.html 204.71.237.87 19970209223215 text/html 8408
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 22:32:58 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 18-Mar-96 19:50:05 GMT
