debunks the medical marijuana argument as well as seven other
myths related to drug abuse.
<P>
15. The author conducted a telephone interview with Gary Fields on
June 27, 1995.
<P>
16. Thomas Huang. &quot;Making Strong Families.&quot;  <I>Chicago
Tribune</I> 2 December 1995:2.
