http://www.atr.org:80/heritage/dept_writeups/gov_for.htm 204.71.237.87 19970209224153 text/html 2576
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 22:42:36 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 26-Jul-96 16:20:04 GMT
Content-length: 2393
