 <li>       This section relies heavily on Patrick F. Fagan, "Rising Illegitimacy: America's Social Catastrophe," Heritage Foundation <i>F.Y.I.</i> No. 19, June 29, 1994. <li>     This sum equals the value of welfare benefits from different programs for the average mother on AFDC.
<li>        Leon Dash, <i>When Children Want Children: An Inside Look at the Crisis of Teenage Parenthood</i> (Penguin Books, 1990).
